data.description:
This 6-bed/7-bath home located in the Broadmoor area is stunning and perfect for a family. 

It’s unique features include an indoor 1/2-court basketball court gym complete w/motorized adjustable basketball hoop, hidden trap door from the kitchen leading to a slide for kids to go down to gym, 21' climbing wal, and outdoor built in trampoline. It has incredible mountain views and a large yard visible from the kitchen.  Main-level master bed has sitting area, walk-in closets, adjoining 5-pc bath, and walkout to ample deck with beautiful mountain views. Other main- level rooms include large open great room with wood-burning fireplace. Spectacular lower level contains gym, large family room and bar, along with an amazing theater room with professional sound system, projector screen, and plush theater furnishings.  There also 4 bedrooms and 4 baths downstairs. This home also has a 4 car garage with 1 bay equipped for a recreational vehicle.
data.whatILove: Our favorite part of this home is the secret door that kids love which takes them down a slide down to the basketball court. This home is perfect for kids!
